Controller

rails g controller homes

会員
rails g controller public/items index show
rails g controller public/cart_items index edit update destroy
rails g controller public/orders index show new create
rails g controller public/addresses index edit create update destroy


管理者
rails g controller admin/items index show edit create update
rails g controller admin/genres index edit create update 
rails g controller admin/order_items update
rails g controller admin/orders index show update


Devise

会員
rails g devise Customer 
rails g devise:controllers customers
rails g devise:views customers

管理者
rails g devise Admin
rails g devise:controllers admins
rails g devise:views admins


Model



アイテムモデル
rails g model Item genre_id:integer price:integer name:string image_id:string explanation:text 

is_order_status:boolean デフォルト値true


ジャンル
rails g model Genres name:string


カート
rails g model Cart_Item item_id:integer user_id:integer quantity:integer 


注文
rails g model Orders user_id:integer payment:integer shipment_charge:integer postal_code:string delivery_address:string delivery_name:string total_price:integer order_status:integer


配送先
rails g Delivery-Addresses user_id:integer address:string postal_code:string name:string


注文商品
rails g Order-Details item_id:integer order_id:integer quantity:integer item_with_tax:integer production_status:integer

